Candela's Restaurant & Pizzeria--Friendly Family Atmosphere.  The food is  excellent.  Favorites are their special chicken dish...Spaghetti with mushrooms, Mussels extra spicy, White Pie with Spinach, Ricotta Cheese, Fresh Garlic  (ask for crispy--The Best!) are just a few of the great cooking done  by Candela's.   Everything  is very good.   Bring your friends and family....Pete and Frank Candela are very accommodating.   You'll love the food.....ALL OF IT!    Buy a gift certificate for someone special ....they will love you for it!!!   Donna-Maria and John
